text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_Fridge {
	format("It's a small fridge...\n"
	"Is this really enough for one person?")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_Sink {
	format("A sink for washing dishes.\n"
	"Does DEVON do this himself every day?")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_Bed {
	format("The bed seems almost too small.\n")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_Commode {
	format("An old commode, where items are arranged neatly.")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_Table {
	format("A very small table. It's probably only enough for a quick snack.")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_Plant {
	format("A simple houseplant.\n"
	"It's well-watered, but could use some high-quality mulch.")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_FirstArrival {
    format("DEVON: Well, here we are!\n"
    "This is my place.\p"
    "I know it's not much, but it's home."
    )
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_FirstArrival2 {
    format("DEVON: We're in the company housing district."
    "It's where all the employees of MAUVILLE MINING live."
    "Or, former employees, in my case...\p"
    "I bought the house from the company with my salary money, so they can't take it away from me now."
    "It's actually all I have now."
    "But I think it was worth it."
    )
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_FirstArrival3 {
    format("DEVON: What about you? What brings you here?"
    "And why were those people after you?"
    )
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_FirstArrival4 {
    format("DEVON: I just realized I only have one chair... That's a bit embarrassing."
    "Why don't you sit down? I'll stand. It's not often I have company."
    )
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_FirstArrival5 {
    format("... ... ...\p"
    "DEVON: So you're the PRINCESS of EVER GRANDE? And you were kidnapped?!\p"
    "By who?"
    "... ... ...\p"
    "You're saying they looked like mining company employees?!"
    )
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_FirstArrival6 {
    format("DEVON: That's strange... And very bad. I can't imagine how frightening that is."
    "I hope you know I'd never sell you out. Is there anything I can do to help?"
    "Maybe there's a way I can help you get back home..."
    )
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_FirstArrival7 {
    format("DEVON: I got it! We can go to SLATEPORT CITY! They have a ferry service."
    "Maybe there's one that'll be departing for EVER GRANDE."
    "I'll get you aboard. And... maybe I can also find a place to go. I really don't want to stay here."
    )
}


text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_Stone1 {
    format("It's a piece of PYRITE.")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_Stone2 {
    format("It's a regular ROCK from Rustboro Caves.")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_StoneEmerald {
    format("It's a fake emerald.")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_DevonsEmerald1 {
    format("DEVON: That's my most prized possession, a real emerald.")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_DevonsEmerald2 {
    format("DEVON: You mean it's fake? It's actually green fluorite...?"
	"That's interesting! You have a sharp eye!"
	"I don't even know what fluorite is... heh. But it all sounds so interesting."
	"I wish I had more time to read up on the natural world, instead of just taking advantage of it."
	)
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_ShowDevonRealEmerald {
    format("You showed DEVON the REAL EMERALD.")
}

text RustboroCity_DevonsHouse_Text_DevonsEmerald3 {
    format("DEVON: So that's a real emerald..."
	"I see, the color is a bit more bluish-green."
	"Thank you for showing me."
	"I guess even though mine's fake, it's still special to me."
	"My father found it by accident when we were walking somewhere. He thought it was real, and so did I."
	"Now it's the only memory I have of him..."
	"Where did you get yours?"
	"So it was a gift from your father as well. I can tell it must be special to you."
	"I promise I'll help you get back to your family."
	)
}